        "action": "Stop fines for taking children out of school on holiday",
        "additional_details": "We want the government to stop the fines for taking our children out of school on holiday and showing them the world without it costing a small fortune that some parents can\u2019t afford! We think holidays are educational. Why should we be fined they are our children.",
